eplyTime":"2017-08-27T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"對鞋入面有紙, 濕左+腳既汁同體溫會有味<br />\n掉左對臭鞋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8179386783ef1d63647ad4535385de46c000f800","tid":376734,"uid":1006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你著涼鞋 呢幾日臭有無濕到水?<br />\n姐係返去途中搞到對鞋濕左</blockquote><br />\n應該除左少少落雨之外無咩可能<br />\n<br />\n但係有幾日無落雨都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fef4c7463bb02f3c0f8f1fd34b7822e79d51071","tid":376734,"uid":73945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"滴露 酒精 漂白水"},{"pid":"554202b30043c71b4afad97ba5999bccf317f820","tid":376734,"uid":41271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你著涼鞋 呢幾日臭有無濕到水?<br />\n姐係返去途中搞到對鞋濕左</blockquote><br />\n應該除左少少落雨之外無咩可能<br />\n<br />\n但係有幾日無落雨都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前試過濕左水無理由佢自己乾就會臭<br />\n應該都關對鞋既事<br />\n你可以試下換另一種質地既鞋<br />\n 濕左要整返乾"},{"pid":"bd788b428dca1f099cbb7a6daaa13b559b820a2c","tid":376734,"uid":1006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你著涼鞋 呢幾日臭有無濕到水?<br />\n姐係返去途中搞到對鞋濕左</blockquote><br />\n應該除左少少落雨之外無咩可能<br />\n<br />\n但係有幾日無落雨都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前試過濕左水無理由佢自己乾就會臭<br />\n應該都關對鞋既事<br />\n你可以試下換另一種質地既鞋<br />\n 濕左要整返乾</blockquote><br />\n點整返乾?<br />\n<br />\n我呢兩日聞到臭味用槻洗左都係就咁瓊返乾佢"},{"pid":"f1d22b40ef09bdcf3b24f601d7321da87f4d9361","tid":376734,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"精神病其中一種"},{"pid":"a3c4fac3b597f0eb31169d6bbf83eb720a90841e","tid":376734,"uid":409,"like":2,"dislike":0